        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The warm, caring light of the sun glows from the center of this magical banner, mirroring the dawn. This magical banner exudes bright light in the banner\u2019s aura (and dim light in an area equal to twice the banner\u2019s aura). This effect is suppressed when you aren\u2019t holding the banner or wielding the weapon it is affixed to.",
